    p
      | Decode72 is a web-based LLC offering design solutions in branding, web design, and mobile and software applications. The company name “Decode72” is a combination of “Design” and “Code” as the three members of the company comprise of a Graphic Designer (Design) and two software developers (Code). The number 72 refers to 72dpi, traditionally the resolution of screen media.
    p
      | The Decode72 website utilizes the latest web technologies such as HTML5, CSS3 and JQuery to create a rich, interactive experience. The site contains four main pages—Home, About Us, Our Work, and Contact—and includes sub-pages showcasing Decode72’s latest projects.
